{"Title":"清爽土豆泥的做法","Primary":["土豆200克"],"Auxiliary":["尖椒1根","洋葱半个","盐1小勺","番茄酱适量"],"Flavoring":[],"Setups":["1.土豆去皮洗干净。切大片放到蒸锅，蒸大约20分钟，蒸熟。","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/51/205/2301301/n2301301_88430.jpg","2.尖椒和洋葱洗干净。","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/51/205/2301301/n2301301_13924.jpg","3.都切成小细粒。","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/51/205/2301301/n2301301_50200.jpg","4.土豆蒸熟取出用勺碾成泥。","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/51/205/2301301/n2301301_51530.jpg","5.放入洋葱和尖椒粒。","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/51/205/2301301/n2301301_94972.jpg","6.放点盐，不要太多，有咸味就可以。","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/51/205/2301301/n2301301_60060.jpg","7.拌匀。","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/51/205/2301301/n2301301_49764.jpg","8.微温后将土豆泥团成乒乓球大小的球。","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/51/205/2301301/n2301301_79405.jpg","9.每个土豆泥小球上挤点番茄酱即可。","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/51/205/2301301/n2301301_54184.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/51/205/2301301/n2301301_20982.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/51/205/2301301/n2301301_87102.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/51/205/2301301/n2301301_82647.jpg","烹饪技巧","盐，不要太多，有咸味就可以。稍微晾一下就可以团成球，有余温时吃最好。"]}